My ads set is showing ready and my ads are active but campaign status is showing warning of no active ads set

It sounds like there might be an issue with the campaign setup. Could you please check if all your ad sets within the campaign are correctly linked and active? Sometimes, even if individual ads are active, the campaign might not recognize them due to a misconfiguration. If everything seems correct and you're still facing issues, I recommend reviewing the ad management settings or reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
